page.title: 18Michelles Day
page.content: I am woken up at seven o'clock by my radio alarm.I get dressed in my school uniform and later I have my breakfast of cornflakes.I brush my hair and clean my teeth, after which I do some reading. I always walk to school.My favourite lesson is Maths.I walk home at 3.30 and watch some television.I often have my tea at 5.30.It is usually a cooked tea because I have a packed lunch at school.A bit later I go to my Auntie's and practise on her piano. Sometimes I do a bit of typing.Later I watch some television. Then I have my supper and clean my teeth and go to bed.
